detailedDescription.articleBody: Yogesh Gaur, commonly credited as Yogesh, was an Indian writer and lyricist. He was known for his contributions to Bollywood, and possibly his best known works came from the film Anand, songs including Kahin Door Jab Din Dal Jaaye and Zindagi Kaisi Hai Paheli, and also Rajnigandha phool tumhare from the movie Rajnigandha.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: योगेश गौर, जिसे आमतौर पर योगेश के रूप में श्रेय दिया जाता है, एक भारतीय लेखक और गीतकार थे, उन्हें बॉलीवुड में उनके योगदान के लिए जाना जाता था, और संभवत: उनकी सबसे प्रसिद्ध रचनाएं फिल्म आनंद से आई थीं, जिनमें कहीं दूर जब दिन दल जाए और जिंदगी कैसी है पहेली शामिल हैं।

detailedDescription.articleBody:
Yogesh 'Yogie' Krishna Chandra Maganti is an Indian director who works in Telugu film industry. He is associated with successful directors Ram Gopal Varma and E. Nivas.
Yogie was born in Eluru, Andhra Pradesh.
He directedOka Raju Oka Rani for Ushakiran Movies.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: योगेश 'योगी' कृष्ण चंद्र मगंती एक भारतीय निर्देशक हैं जो तेलुगु फिल्म उद्योग में काम करते हैं, वे सफल निर्देशकों राम गोपाल वर्मा और ई, निवास के साथ जुड़े हुए हैं।\n

detailedDescription.articleBody: Lieutenant General Yogesh Kumar Joshi, UYSM, AVSM, VrC, SM, ADC is a serving General Officer in the Indian Army. He is the current General Officer Commanding-in-Chief Northern Command, assuming office from Lt Gen Ranbir Singh on 1 February 2020.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: लेफ्टिनेंट जनरल योगेश कुमार जोशी, यूवाईएसएम, एवीएसएम, वीआरसी, एसएम, एडीसी भारतीय सेना में एक सेवारत जनरल ऑफिसर हैं, वे वर्तमान जनरल ऑफिसर कमांडिंग-इन-चीफ उत्तरी कमान हैं, जो 1 फरवरी 2020 को लेफ्टिनेंट जनरल रणबीर सिंह से पदभार ग्रहण कर रहे हैं।

detailedDescription.articleBody:
Yogesh is an Indian actor and singer who predominantly appears in Kannada language films.
Yogesh made his debut in the 2007 film Duniya where he portrayed the supporting character named "Loose Maada" and since then being referred with the same name.

detailedDescription.articleBody: Yogeshwar Dutt is an Indian freestyle wrestler. At the 2012 Summer Olympics, he won the bronze medal in the 60 kg category. He was awarded the Padma Shri by the Government of India in 2013. He won a gold medal at the 2014 Commonwealth Games.
